{
  "stem": "26983.11",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 23.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was whole procedure how they've done it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were living in different compounds of course, and they left the soup under the bed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You must imagine, only in a block which was more or less in better condition, somebody left his ration of soup--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--it would be impossible to do it in Auschwitz or in late in Birkenau or in the Mauthausen between us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the old prisoners had their own blocks where their situation was much better.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he told us I go to work but I leave you children some soup.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a whole job to get out of our block of our courtyard, but we managed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we took the soup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we brought it to our camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Once it was me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember the greatest temptation in my life was that I had now this soup and I had to share it--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A pot-- I don't know, a little soup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But at that time, it was like gold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I knew everyone had four spoons let's say, of soup.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could divide it between our little group of children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had my four spoons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was able to finish the whole soup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was able to eat five spoons and it was the greatest temptation in my life not to do it and to share it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because it's very difficult to imagine what it is if you're in such a situation and have food to share it with somebody else.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we still had this kind of--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Much worse.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, people were dying of hunger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even the beginning wasn't so bad to say months or two months later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I speak now about the end of--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--January, beginning of February.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a sadist blockeldester.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He took our rations.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
